{"tid":2141573,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(求安慰) 談紀念日的重要性","createTime":"2020-08-05T19:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:58:40.000Z","uid":250093,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"95f40c2e33f3a4648c2b5ec5a90c903b6c81cb0c","tid":2141573,"uid":250093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:49:34.000Z","msg":"如題: <br />\n琴日5號 係我哋相識一周年紀念日<br />\n之前有講過話 唔好特別大搞 (你明的)<br />\n見過面食餐飯就算  <br />\n<br />\n跟住兩三個星期前 知道佢個日 要見大老細 <br />\n都有同佢講話不如第二日先慶祝<br />\n然後佢話唔使 嗰日放工就可以見 <br />\n跟住 呢幾日佢總共發咗3次脾氣 <br />\n(呢幾日都冇問我紀念日想點處理)<br />\n前日佢見之前 話自己唔知點準備 跟住發我脾氣 <br />\n明明佢好早就知道又唔早啲準備 <br />\n佢話 自己冇時間休息同準備 因為上個weekend嚟咗陪我<br />\n跟住前晚收線 我唔開心咗好耐 喊到朝頭早先瞓  <br />\n<br />\n結果琴日佢個會面is a casual one <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後夜晚佢就同我講 一年快樂 跟住先問我點慶祝 <br />\n到佢放工打嚟 又冇乜點出聲 喺度打機 <br />\n跟住我就收佢線 佢話夜啲搵返我 <br />\n跟住我已經sad sad 地 就同佢講 算啦聽日先啦你打機啦今日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真心想問其實係咪我對待呢啲日子認真咗"},{"pid":"5c7a9785e4bc0422275811e75e93c6a70515a2b5","tid":2141573,"uid":335303,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:51:03.000Z","msg":"分手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>未睇內文</code>"},{"pid":"5668607c00642d4d31da03d1c0037c0d5fa09430","tid":2141573,"uid":250093,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:52:48.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮我喎 都係想圍下爐姐"},{"pid":"d5a96840a7b4a495d3f89f8613a846dac16657f5","tid":2141573,"uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:53:52.000Z","msg":"諗起紀念日果晚收帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1a23631e8b8e2f90cbfa23ae1aea8f4a4e1873","tid":2141573,"uid":251851,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:55:10.000Z","msg":"拍拖紀念都唔慶祝下<br />\n咁拍黎都無乜意思<br />\n無準備 但只少都要一齊過呀"},{"pid":"e22518aa8c2184ae9c889ac8a51fe38a4e965af5","tid":2141573,"uid":260581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:56:11.000Z","msg":"琴日5號 三年前分手<br />\n你都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd996925c14f2ff3bef6912ca596d248a1349ea","tid":2141573,"uid":250093,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"3e1a23631e8b8e2f90cbfa23ae1aea8f4a4e1873","tid":2141573,"uid":251851,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:55:10.000Z","msg":"拍拖紀念都唔慶祝下<br />\n咁拍黎都無乜意思<br />\n無準備 但只少都要一齊過呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係拍拖紀念嚟嘅只係相識紀念 <br />\n同埋平時都唔係每個月慶祝 <br />\n所以我都唔知係咪其實我認真咗"},{"pid":"5c7eaa9652614d2043b9963ef0f8e8490b9811e2","tid":2141573,"uid":251851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afd996925c14f2ff3bef6912ca596d248a1349ea","tid":2141573,"uid":250093,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"3e1a23631e8b8e2f90cbfa23ae1aea8f4a4e1873","tid":2141573,"uid":251851,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:55:10.000Z","msg":"拍拖紀念都唔慶祝下<br />\n咁拍黎都無乜意思<br />\n無準備 但只少都要一齊過呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係拍拖紀念嚟嘅只係相識紀念 <br />\n同埋平時都唔係每個月慶祝 <br />\n所以我都唔知係咪其實我認真咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:01:36.000Z","msg":"咁要睇你定義啦 姐係你覺得重要 而對方覺得唔重要 就要拎出嚟講 攞個共識 如果唔係 你會無哂期望"},{"pid":"f79244e46481e75564629ed246d897337ff8ee81","tid":2141573,"uid":132898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c7eaa9652614d2043b9963ef0f8e8490b9811e2","tid":2141573,"uid":251851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afd996925c14f2ff3bef6912ca596d248a1349ea","tid":2141573,"uid":250093,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"3e1a23631e8b8e2f90cbfa23ae1aea8f4a4e1873","tid":2141573,"uid":251851,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:55:10.000Z","msg":"拍拖紀念都唔慶祝下<br />\n咁拍黎都無乜意思<br />\n無準備 但只少都要一齊過呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實都唔係拍拖紀念嚟嘅只係相識紀念 <br />\n同埋平時都唔係每個月慶祝 <br />\n所以我都唔知係咪其實我認真咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:01:36.000Z","msg":"咁要睇你定義啦 姐係你覺得重要 而對方覺得唔重要 就要拎出嚟講 攞個共識 如果唔係 你會無哂期望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T22:25:22.000Z","msg":"真 有共識好重要"},{"pid":"3239f3ff77578370a8c6447d2261981e9168352c","tid":2141573,"uid":103248,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:32:46.000Z","msg":"相識又要慶祝 拍拖又要慶祝 聖誕又要慶祝 情人節又要慶祝 生日又要慶祝 乜都要慶祝既一年咪要慶成十幾次祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9d9540cde9fb34b49db9a8cf359a1d332865cd","tid":2141573,"uid":241643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:53:04.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得自己一個認真上心<br />\n<br />\n啫係咁講絲打，佢未係最差，至少佢會打個電話嚟同你講一年快樂，雖然繼續打機連諗都唔諗下點預備真係過分咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得，既然你知佢嗰排燥底又忙又攰嘅話，咁你都唔好期望佢會為個紀念日準備得好周全先。如果係咁不如你準備多啲，然後係前一兩日比個plan佢睇問佢咁好唔好。我第一年嘅拍拖紀念日都冇同男朋友去邊/做咩，剩係喺佢屋企睇咗齣戲之後喺埋人度食咗餐好簡單嘅飯。<br />\n<br />\n你同佢講返依件事令你唔開心未？"},{"pid":"17e16ff2b1adc1d77a133b3c8d875f2af18af53e","tid":2141573,"uid":202898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T01:52:00.000Z","msg":"快d同佢分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放過人啦"},{"pid":"b4c4aa686ad0f0ce2c62333fe6c3c8e5228c8195","tid":2141573,"uid":69275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"相識週年，一齊週年，結婚週年，情人節，白色情人節，七夕，聖誕，你生日，佢生日，一年慶祝咁撚多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d1138047997fdc0e580c758f058940b57a61f5","tid":2141573,"uid":131746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"相識都要慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇拖手紀念日同扑野紀念日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69869d0e9988802b9af624d8d7c3f4c5cb6b5ce3","tid":2141573,"uid":192409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得就唔使太過看重呢啲紀念日, 只要你感覺到個男仔係真心鍾意你 對你好咪夠晒囉, 未必個個男仔咁浪漫同對呢啲紀念日咁上心 咁當係一回事架"},{"pid":"dfd80c4988827ec17dce567cfc34abb922134756","tid":2141573,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d1138047997fdc0e580c758f058940b57a61f5","tid":2141573,"uid":131746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"相識都要慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇拖手紀念日同扑野紀念日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"打茄輪 含撚 中出 69 <br />\n日日都是紀念日"},{"pid":"e9469ec7e1512a00e9086c24a62575fd459b3c8a","tid":2141573,"uid":176148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac39e0393de32a8add300d6a776a31b2cd00c9a","tid":2141573,"uid":120418,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"又係你話唔好大搞,而家人地無特別準備又唔高興<br />\n咁調返轉,你有冇為呢個紀念日準備咩先?<br />\n下下都係對方諗,對方付出<br />\n佢忙你咪幫佢諗下去邊食飯/點慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe66a247cb6fe6ab7df836d0b7ac5c44e18ec55","tid":2141573,"uid":21187,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"共識咗每個紀念日都會一齊過 講緊係每個月<br />\n黎緊半年了 佢要陪屋企人 少少失望咁<br />\n但我之前都因為要出席一個重要聚會而無陪佢<br />\n不過其實每日都係獨一無二既 當休息下算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信時間越耐會越唔CARE呢啲野<br />\n但雙方生日, 週年紀念就點都依然係重要日子"},{"pid":"eaa6de77c2480e55c9a34a715a916ffd0cde261f","tid":2141573,"uid":250093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac39e0393de32a8add300d6a776a31b2cd00c9a","tid":2141573,"uid":120418,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"又係你話唔好大搞,而家人地無特別準備又唔高興<br />\n咁調返轉,你有冇為呢個紀念日準備咩先?<br />\n下下都係對方諗,對方付出<br />\n佢忙你咪幫佢諗下去邊食飯/點慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"準備咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本諗住接佢收工 點知前晚佢發我脾氣"},{"pid":"b68dde367b7d1b667b9ad703a86aff445bf47720","tid":2141573,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"分手囉"},{"pid":"c79966261caef66bed68fd60b93b58b8ae06836d","tid":2141573,"uid":75597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"好小事姐<br />\n明知佢忙咪改過第二日<br />\n<br />\n利申從不慶祝呢啲野"},{"pid":"ee17c2929df9ae6ff9afbc505b88d7c3e15dcd9a","tid":2141573,"uid":261729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5a96840a7b4a495d3f89f8613a846dac16657f5","tid":2141573,"uid":203701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T19:53:52.000Z","msg":"諗起紀念日果晚收帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"你又真係慘啲"},{"pid":"29fe5da856804b7274917b402ea0da23d2136ef5","tid":2141573,"uid":261729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,